
'''基本醫療保險福利'''（{{lang-en|Essential health benefits}}，EHBs）是在2010年通過的《[[患者保護與平價醫療法案|患者保護與平價醫療法案]]》（PPACA，或稱 ACA）所規定的一組包含10項的保險福利，在美國{{le|個人自行購買的醫療保險|Individually purchased health insurance in the United States}}以及小型雇主團體保險的保單裡面都必須包含這些福利（无论是否在[[醫療保險市集|醫療保險市集]]之内或之外購買）。大型團體醫療保險計劃、還有根據{{link-en|1974年僱員退休所得安全法|Employee Retirement Income Security Act of 1974}}（ERISA）設立的[[自籌資金醫療保險計畫|自籌資金醫療保險計畫]]、以及經由ERISA管理的多重僱主福利措施（這些均不受美國各州{{link-en|保險法|insurance law}}約束），則不受EHBs的要求限制。<ref name=rose>Sara Rosenbaum, Joel Teitelbaum & Katherine Hayes, [http://www.commonwealthfund.org/~/media/Files/Publications/Issue%20Brief/2011/Mar/1485_Rosenbaum_essential_hlt_benefits_provisions_ACA_disabilities_reform_brief_v2.pdf The Essential Health Benefits Provisions of the Affordable Care Act: Implications for People with Disabilities] {{Wayback|url=http://www.commonwealthfund.org/~/media/Files/Publications/Issue%20Brief/2011/Mar/1485_Rosenbaum_essential_hlt_benefits_provisions_ACA_disabilities_reform_brief_v2.pdf |date=20161020192015 }}, [[Commonwealth_Fund|Commonwealth Fund]] (March 2011).</ref>{{rp|3}}

==定義==
PPACA 在法案的第1302（b）（1）節中訂下10種基本醫療保險福利，<ref>[https://www.healthcare.gov/blog/10-health-care-benefits-covered-in-the-health-insurance-marketplace/ 10 health care benefits covered in the Health Insurance Marketplace] {{Wayback|url=https://www.healthcare.gov/blog/10-health-care-benefits-covered-in-the-health-insurance-marketplace/ |date=20200812205845 }}, HealthCare.gov (accessed November 12, 2015).</ref><ref name="FamiliesUSA">Alexandra Ernst, [http://familiesusa.org/blog/10-essential-health-benefits-insurance-plans-must-cover-starting-in-2014 10 Essential Health Benefits Insurance Plans Must Cover Starting in 2014] {{Wayback|url=http://familiesusa.org/blog/10-essential-health-benefits-insurance-plans-must-cover-starting-in-2014 |date=20180129182104 }}, FamiliesUSA  (March 28, 2013).</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Folger|first1=Jean|title=Essential Health Benefits Under The Affordable Care Act|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/investopedia/2013/10/11/essential-health-benefits-under-the-affordable-care-act/#e8741243633c|accessdate=July 28, 2017|publisher=Forbes Magazine|date=October 11, 2013|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20170728215424/https://www.forbes.com/sites/investopedia/2013/10/11/essential-health-benefits-under-the-affordable-care-act/%23e8741243633c#e8741243633c|archivedate=2017-07-28|url-status=dead|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並將它們列入[[美國法典|美國法典]]第42條  §18022（b）之中：<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.law.cornell.edu/uscode/text/42/18022 |title=42 U.S. Code § 18022 - Essential health benefits requirements |accessdate=2020-08-26 |archive-date=2020-09-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200910153448/https://www.law.cornell.edu/uscode/text/42/18022 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
